trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of documents discovered during XML Web services discovery that have been downloaded to the client.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de documentos descobertos durante a descoberta de serviços Web em XML que foram baixados para o cliente.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> propriedade <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> é do tipo <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The following code example enacts XML Web service discovery and downloads the discovered documents to the client.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir aplica a descoberta de serviço da Web em XML e baixa os documentos de descoberta para o cliente.

trans-unit.source: The names of the discovery documents within the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection> are output to the console.
trans-unit.target: Os nomes dos documentos de descoberta dentro de <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection> são enviadas ao console.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL for the document to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL do documento a ser adicionado à <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A discovered document to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um documento descoberto a ser adicionado à <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds an object with the specified URL to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um objeto com a URL especificada à <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The following code example adds two discovery documents to a <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir adiciona dois documentos de descoberta para um <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An entry with a key of <paramref name="url" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma entrada com uma chave <paramref name="url" /> já existe no <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL for the document to locate within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL do documento a ser localizado na <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> contains an object with the specified URL.
trans-unit.target: Determina se a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> contém um objeto com a URL especificada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> contains an object with the specified URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> contém um objeto com a URL especificada; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The following code example calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection.Contains%2A> method to determine if the discovery document contains a member with the URL stored in the `StringUrl` variable.
trans-unit.target: O código a seguir exemplo chama o <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection.Contains%2A> método para determinar se o documento de descoberta contém um membro com a URL armazenada no `StringUrl` variável.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the discovery document to get or set from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL do documento de descoberta a ser obtido ou baixado da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a client discovery document object from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> with the specified URL.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um objeto de documento de descoberta de cliente da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" /> com a URL especificada.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> representing the document discovered and downloaded to the client.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Object" /> que representa o documento de descoberta e baixado no cliente.

trans-unit.source: The underlying type of the object can be a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" />, <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema" />, or <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument" />.
trans-unit.target: O tipo subjacente do objeto pode ser um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" />, <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema" />, ou <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument" />.

trans-unit.source: The following code example outputs to the console the type of the discovery document in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection> that has a URL matching the value of the `myStringUrl` variable.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir gera para o console do tipo do documento de descoberta no <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection> que tem uma URL de correspondência do valor da `myStringUrl` variável.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object with all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> com todas as chaves na <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the keys of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém as chaves do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir gera chaves dentro de <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection> para o console.

trans-unit.source: The URL for the discovered document to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL para o documento de descoberta a ser removido da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes an object with the specified URL from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Remove um objeto com a URL especificada da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The following code example removes the discovery document with a URL of `http://www.contoso.com/service1.disco` from the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir remove o documento de descoberta com a URL `http://www.contoso.com/service1.disco` do <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object with all the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> com todos os valores na <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém os valores de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection" />.
